<I>Cf.</I> Aristotle, <I>Rhetoric</I>, <SPAN CLASS="small">III</SPAN>.1017, p1411<SPAN CLASS="small">A</SPAN>; said by the Athenian orator Leptines, in opposing the destruction of Sparta, one of the "eyes of Greece."


