onMouseOut="nd();">65</A>
	<A HREF="
https://archive.org/stream/tragicorumgraeco00naucuoft#page/675/mode/2up
	"TARGET="offsite"
onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,2,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">
Nauck, <I>Trag. Graec. Frag.</I> p675, no. 974.
	</A>
From an unknown play, quoted also
	<A HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Plutarch/Moralia/De_cohibenda_ira*.html#T464a
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,0,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">
<I>Moralia</I>, 464<SPAN CLASS="small">A</SPAN></A>.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note66" HREF="
