"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">67</A>
The length was twenty stadia, slightly more than two and a quarter miles.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note68" HREF="
