815<SPAN CLASS="small">D</SPAN>
	</A>
and Lucian, <I>Iuppiter Tragoedus</I>, chap. li<!--</A>LUCIAN--> and scholium.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
