"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">80</A>
Arcadia and Rhodes especially. Polybius was a statesman and historian, Panaetius a Stoic philosopher.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note81" HREF="
